	<h1>AUTHORIZATION OF UNITED MOTOR CARRIER COOPERATIVE</h1>
	<p>That, ________________________, LLC, a Utah limited liability company and/or <?=$fullname?>, an individual (collectively the "Motor Carrier"), as a member of United Motor Carrier Cooperative, LCA, a Utah limited cooperative association (the "Cooperative") does hereby authorize and empower the Cooperative's President, Garrett Barber, to act for, and in the name and place of, the undersigned in all matters connected with the powers specified below:</p>
	<p>1. To request, ask, demand, sue for, recover, collect, receive, and hold and possess all such sums of money due and owing to the Motor Carrier for collection management by the Cooperative pursuant to Cooperative documents.</p>
	<p>2. To communicate with any insurance companies of the Motor Carrier and/or the Motor Carrier's contractors regarding insurance matters, including obtaining insurances and updating insurance policies on behalf of the Motor Carrier, designating the Motor Carrier and/or its members in the capacities of drivers, managers, members, owners, financial guarantors, CEOs, presidents, additional insured, loss payees or any other role required concerning these purposes.</p>
	<p>3. To purchase, or lease as applicable, for and on behalf of the Motor Carrier or to coordinate the purchase or lease for the Motor Carrier fuel, insurance, equipment facilities, administrative and professional services.</p>
	<p>4. The rights, powers, and authority granted herein granted shall commence and be in full force and effect as of the date hereof, and such rights, powers, and authority shall remain in full force and effect hereafter until terminated by a writing executed and acknowledged by the Motor Carrier.</p>
	<p>IN WITNESS WHEREOF, the Motor Carrier executes this Authorization this <?=date('jS',strtotime($date))?> day of <?=date('F',strtotime($date))?>, <?=date('Y',strtotime($date))?>.</p>
